                     <interp inst="t18301209-26-person346" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am bailiff to William Mellish, Esq., of <placeName id="t18301209-26-crimeloc159">Bush-hill Park</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18301209-26-crimeloc159" type="placeName" value="Bush-hill Park"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18301209-26-crimeloc159" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-26-off156 t18301209-26-crimeloc159"></join>. The prisoner was a <rs id="t18301209-26-deflabel160" type="occupation">thresher</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-26-defend341 t18301209-26-deflabel160"></join>, and had been threshing wheat that day - I have looked at this wheat, and believe it to be Mr. Mellish's, and likewise that found at the prisoner's house; I have compared them with the bulk at Mr. Mellish's - the prisoner has not worked for any body else for a year and a half.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18301209-26-verdict161" type="verdictDescription">
